                        <p>One of the most heartbreaking thing we have heard over the years from couples is that they loved us, but that we were simply out of their photography budget. This has really stuck with us, so we have decided to focus on just what is essential to ensure our couple’s photographs are amazing. We use top of the line cameras, lenses, and lights; and we have insurance and full backups.  Every decision we make, we ask ourselves is this improves the experience of couples working with Dogwood Photography. We are not budget photography, but we are trying to be affordable photography.</p>
                        <p>At Dogwood, we understand the frustration of trying to find the perfect photographer for your wedding, so we put everything up front and easy to find.  We put our photography pricing right on the website, so you can make an informed decision about your wedding photography needs.  We have moved everything online from contract signage to image delivery to not only reduce paper usage, but to make it super simple for you!</p>
